         <abstract id="aspace_4c64cccea4919e3e56dc388072bba4d7">The materials, compiled by Steven Bergman, consist of unorganized reports, publications, newspapers, clippings, and photographs documenting the history of the School of Management. The controversy surrounding the appointment of Michael E. Levine as dean of the school in 1988 is particularly well documented.</abstract>
